 {"id":"bd-3tmk","title":"Notification/Toast System with Queue Management","description":"## Background

Almost every application needs to show transient feedback:
- 'File saved successfully'
- 'Network error: connection refused'
- '3 items deleted'
- 'Copied to clipboard'

Currently, FrankenTUI has no built-in notification system. Developers must implement their own, leading to inconsistent UX.

## Unique Challenge: Inline Mode

In inline mode, notifications must not corrupt scrollback. This is a unique challenge that FrankenTUI is well-positioned to solve correctly.

## Solution: NotificationManager + NotificationStack Widget

```rust
#[derive(Debug, Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq)]
pub enum NotificationLevel {
    Info,
    Success,
    Warning,
    Error,
}

#[derive(Debug, Clone)]
pub struct Notification {
    pub id: NotificationId,
    pub level: NotificationLevel,
    pub title: Option<String>,
    pub message: String,
    pub duration: Option<Duration>,  // None = persistent
    pub dismissable: bool,
    pub action: Option<NotificationAction>,
    pub created_at: Instant,
}

pub struct NotificationAction {
    pub label: String,
    pub callback: Box<dyn FnOnce() + Send>,
}

#[derive(Debug, Clone, Copy)]
pub enum NotificationPosition {
    TopRight,
    TopLeft,
    BottomRight,
    BottomLeft,
    TopCenter,
    BottomCenter,
}

pub struct NotificationManager {
    queue: VecDeque<Notification>,
    max_visible: usize,        // Default: 5
    position: NotificationPosition,
    default_duration: Duration, // Default: 5s
    stacking: StackDirection,   // Up or Down
}

impl NotificationManager {
    pub fn notify(&mut self, notification: Notification) -> NotificationId;
    pub fn info(&mut self, message: &str) -> NotificationId;
    pub fn success(&mut self, message: &str) -> NotificationId;
    pub fn warning(&mut self, message: &str) -> NotificationId;
    pub fn error(&mut self, message: &str) -> NotificationId;
    pub fn dismiss(&mut self, id: NotificationId);
    pub fn dismiss_all(&mut self);
    pub fn tick(&mut self, now: Instant) -> Vec<NotificationId>; // Expired
}

// Widget for rendering
pub struct NotificationStack<'a> {
    manager: &'a NotificationManager,
    theme: &'a NotificationTheme,
}

impl Widget for NotificationStack<'_> {
    fn render(&self, area: Rect, frame: &mut Frame);
}
```

